original_title: They Might Be Giants: Them Ain't Big Eye Ants
overview: This disc spotlights TMBG videos from 2001-2012. Amazing animations and rock videos, including rare Home Movies and Homestar Runner clips! This is a must-have document for all TMBG fans.
tagline: YouTube videos look better when there's a DVD on the shelf next to your computer!
title: They Might Be Giants: Them Ain't Big Eye Ants
